Version 0.3
- Can log the info on directories instead of using repos
- Allows to set directories and exclude variables on the config file 
- removed mysqldb dependencies
- clear email information

Version 0.2
- Migrated from SVN to Git. SVN is not supported anymore (sorry!)
- Able to read mysql servers list from an AWS tag
- Friendly names for servers (instead of DNS or IP)
- It can run as root


Version 0.1
- Using SVN repo
- Tracking table schema changes
- Tracking users permissions
- Tracking mysql variables


